snippet.title: Alchemical INC. | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Alchemical INC. wraps a card auto battler in an immersive first person adventure. Explore the mean steampunk streets of New Folk City. Trade your cards to craft the perfect deck or else you're going home empty handed.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1609740/Alchemical_INC/

Upcoming Kickstarter on March 15th: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/alchemical-inc/alchemical-inc

Follow us for updates:
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/Eaf5UrHU2e
Twitter: https://twitter.com/loochlabs
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/loochlabs
